range_partition - package range_partition
 
range_partition - Class in range_partition
It partitions a GPS data collection of cows into three periods (pre-day, daytime, post-day) based on a given time file Input: files name of GPS and time data Output: three time partition files
range_partition() - Constructor for class range_partition.range_partition
 
range_pixel - package range_pixel
 
range_pixel - Class in range_pixel
Given the pixel file that contains the range geographic information and the GPS records, it calculate the percent grazed pixels, and pixel residence time, revisit rate (visits on different days), and return interval (interval between visits when cows visited the same pixel for more than once) by considering the velocity of the cow.
